![Crypto_project drawio](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c7c87d47-6906-4c50-a7a1-8053dc327734)# ü™ô Real-Time Crypto Analytics Platform

A full-stack real-time cryptocurrency analytics platform combining **data engineering**, **machine learning**, and **interactive dashboards** ‚Äî featuring anomaly detection, time-series forecasting, and sentiment analysis.


---

## üöÄ Overview

This project ingests **live cryptocurrency data** from [CoinGecko](https://coingecko.com) and [Alternative.me (Fear & Greed Index)](https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/), performs real-time ETL, applies ML models for anomaly detection and forecasting, and visualizes insights in a beautiful dashboard using **Dash** and **Streamlit**.

> üîÅ Built for end-to-end data flow: `Kafka ‚Üí Spark ‚Üí PostgreSQL ‚Üí Airflow ‚Üí ML ‚Üí Dash`

## üîß Tech Stack

| Layer          | Technologies Used                                      |
|----------------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| **Ingestion**   | Kafka, Python Kafka Producer, CoinGecko API            |
| **ETL**         | Apache Spark Structured Streaming, PySpark             |
| **Database**    | PostgreSQL (Bronze, Silver, Anomaly, Sentiment Layers) |
| **ML Models**   | Isolation Forest, Prophet (Forecasting), LOF (Planned) |
| **Scheduler**   | Apache Airflow                                         |
| **Dashboard**   | Dash (Plotly), Streamlit                               |
| **Infra**       | AWS EC2, systemd                     |

---

## üìä Features

‚úÖ Real-time crypto price streaming from CoinGecko  
‚úÖ Spark Streaming-based ETL to PostgreSQL  
‚úÖ Anomaly detection using Isolation Forest  
‚úÖ Time-series price forecasting using Prophet  
‚úÖ Sentiment analysis via Fear & Greed Index API  
‚úÖ Interactive Dash dashboard with:
- üìà Price & anomaly overlay
- üîÆ Forecast prediction
- üåô Dark mode
- üì• CSV download
- üé≠ Date range picker  
‚úÖ Streamlit version available with heatmaps and autorefresh

---

---

## üìà ML Capabilities

### üîç Anomaly Detection

- **Model**: Isolation Forest (`scikit-learn`)
- **Input Features**:
  - `avg_price`
  - `avg_volume`
  - `market_cap`
  - `24h price change %`
- **Labeling**: Normal (1), Anomaly (-1)
- **Storage**: Stored in `anomaly.<coin>_anomalies`

> üìå Supports expansion to LOF or One-Class SVM

### üìâ Forecasting

- **Model**: [Facebook Prophet](https://facebook.github.io/prophet/)
- **Predicted Feature**: Future `avg_price`
- **Visuals**:
  - Forecast line with 95% confidence bounds
- **Storage**: `silver_crypto.forecast_price`

---

## üò± Sentiment Analysis

- Source: [Alternative.me Crypto Fear & Greed Index](https://alternative.me/crypto/fear-and-greed-index/)
- API: `https://api.alternative.me/fng/`
- Stored to: `sentiment_crypto.fear_greed_index`
- Dashboard Integration: Dual Y-axis chart (price + sentiment)

---

## üì∫ Dash UI Highlights

- üåô **Dark Mode** toggle  
- üîÆ **Show Forecast** toggle  
- üìâ Price + anomaly markers  
- üì§ Export CSV  
- üìÖ Date filtering  
- üìä Fear & Greed sentiment overlay  
- ü™ô Logo-rich dropdown with 5 top coins (BTC, ETH, USDT, XRP, SOL)
